  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db4\u0dd2 \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dc0 \u0da2\u0db1\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dc5\u0dda \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0dcf \u0db6\u0dc0 \u0daf\u0dd0\u0db1\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We made Ranil the president knowing where",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Urban Development and Housing Minister Mr. Prasanna Ranatunga said in the budget debate today (2) that President Ranil was allowed to lay his eggs in our nest without knowing where.",
        "Therefore, he said that coho's eggs are protected and the caterpillars that come to eat the eggs are killed.",
        "\"The members of the opposition who participated in the debate in the past few days talked about the way out of this crisis. A way to isolate the President and get out of their political crisis by hitting Pohottuwa and Rajapaksa. Today, the President has become good for them, and we have become villains after the President was appointed.",
        "They don't remember how they left the current president. The President invited them to forget all that and think about the country and rescue the country from the crisis. Today, this opposition compares him to someone who laid eggs in the crow's nest. Remember that it is the first time that we are told that the flowers will bloom and the years will come.",
        "Yes, we gave our nest to lay eggs there. We gave willingly. He told me where. So we are not going to cut corners. The President and we are working together. That is the System Change. He first tried to make drugs with you.",
        "It was you who killed him and drove him away. We are grateful for the commitment made by Ministers Harin and Manusha after understanding the crisis. Remember that we are the ones who keep the eggs of Koha. We will kill the nymphs who come to eat those eggs. They will not eat eggs.\""
      ],
